// Advent of Code __YEAR__, Day __DAY__
// https://adventofcode.com/__YEAR__/day/__DAY__
//
// TDD flow:
//   1. Paste the puzzle's example into sample.txt.
//   2. Set the two `part_ sample` expectations below to the example's stated
//      answers and run `make test YEAR=__YEAR__` — they start red.
//   3. Implement parse / part1 / part2 until the sample passes.
//   4. `make pull` + `make solve` to get the real answers, then record them in
//      the `part_ input` expectations to lock in a regression.

use lib.aoc
use assert
use runner

